---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="MNL Innovation - Web Development"
	keywords="Web Development, SEO"
	description="IT solutions provider dedicated to helping businesses evolve through technology. We deliver end-to-end IT services—from infrastructure design and cybersecurity to software development and strategic consulting."
>
	<div class="bg-white mt-20">
		<main
			class="mx-auto px-4 pb-24 pt-14 sm:px-6 sm:pb-32 sm:pt-16 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8"
		>
			<!-- Product -->
			<div
				class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-7 lg:grid-rows-1 lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-10 xl:gap-x-16"
			>
				<!-- Product image -->
				<div class="lg:col-span-4 lg:row-end-1">
					<div
						class="aspect-h-3 aspect-w-4 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
					>
						<img
							src="/images/products/website.webp"
							alt="Web development"
							class="object-cover object-center bg-repeat"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Product details -->
				<div
					class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-2xl sm:mt-16 lg:col-span-3 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-end-2 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none"
				>
					<div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
						<div class="mt-4">
							<h1
								class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-3xl"
							>
								Web Development
							</h1>

							<h2 id="information-heading" class="sr-only">Web Development</h2>
						</div>
					</div>

					<p class="mt-6 text-gray-500">
						Web development is the process of building and maintaining websites
						and web applications. It covers everything from simple landing pages
						and blogs. Web development blends programming, design, and server
						management to create fast, functional, and visually engaging
						experiences for users on desktops and mobile devices.
					</p>

					<div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-6 gap-y-4 sm:grid-cols-1">
						<a
							href="/contact"
							class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border bg-[#00629E] px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white hover:bg-[#00629E] hover:text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2"
						>
							Contact
						</a>
					</div>

					<!-- Lista de servicios -->
					<div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
						<h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">
							Key Features of Our Web Development Approach
						</h3>
						<div class="prose prose-sm mt-4 text-gray-500">
							<ul role="list" class="space-y-6">
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-gray-300"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Responsive Design:</strong> Websites that look and
											perform great across all devices.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-gray-300"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Fast Performance:</strong> Optimized loading speed
											for improved user experience and SEO.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-gray-300"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Scalable Architecture:</strong> Designed to grow with
											your business needs.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-gray-300"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Modern Aesthetics:</strong> Clean, user-friendly UI/UX
											designs.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-gray-300"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>SEO Ready:</strong> Structured code and content to
											rank better on search engines.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-gray-300"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Security Best Practices:</strong> SSL encryption,
											secure data handling, and protection from common vulnerabilities.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div
					class="mx-auto mt-16 w-full max-w-2xl lg:col-span-4 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none"
				>
					<div>
						<div class="border-b border-gray-200">
							<div
								class="-mb-px flex space-x-8"
								aria-orientation="horizontal"
								role="tablist"
							>
								<button
									id="tab-faq"
									class="border-transparent text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300 hover:text-gray-800 whitespace-nowrap border-b-2 py-6 text-sm font-medium"
									aria-controls="tab-panel-faq"
									role="tab"
									type="button"
									>We leverage modern frameworks and platforms to build fast,
									maintainable, and scalable websites.
								</button>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div
							id="tab-panel-faq"
							class="text-sm text-gray-500"
							aria-labelledby="tab-faq"
							role="tabpanel"
							tabindex="0"
						>
							<h3 class="sr-only">Technologies We Use</h3>

							<div
								id="tab-panel-faq"
								class="text-sm text-gray-500"
								aria-labelledby="tab-faq"
								role="tabpanel"
								tabindex="0"
							>
								<h3 class="sr-only">Technologies We Use</h3>

								<dl>
									<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
										<strong>Astro:</strong> A cutting-edge, static-site generator
										that delivers lightning-fast performance by shipping less JavaScript.
										Ideal for content-rich websites, blogs, portfolios, and marketing
										pages.
									</dt>

									<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
										<strong>Vercel:</strong> A cloud platform for frontend frameworks
										and static sites, optimized for performance and easy deployment.
										Perfect for hosting Astro apps with global CDN and seamless integration
										with Git.
									</dt>

									<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
										<strong>React, Vue, Svelte:</strong> Component-based libraries
										for building interactive UIs.
									</dt>
									<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
										<strong>Tailwind CSS:</strong> Utility-first CSS framework for
										rapid UI development.
									</dt>
									<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
										<strong>Node.js & Express:</strong> Robust backend support for
										API and server-side logic.Node.js & Express: Robust backend support
										for API and server-side logic.
									</dt>
								</dl>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div
					class="mx-auto mt-16 w-full max-w-2xl lg:col-span-4 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none"
				>
					<div>
						<div class="border-b border-gray-200">
							<div
								class="-mb-px flex space-x-8"
								aria-orientation="horizontal"
								role="tablist"
							>
								<button
									id="tab-faq"
									class="border-transparent text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300 hover:text-gray-800 whitespace-nowrap border-b-2 py-6 text-sm font-medium"
									aria-controls="tab-panel-faq"
									role="tab"
									type="button"
									>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
								</button>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div
							id="tab-panel-faq"
							class="text-sm text-gray-500"
							aria-labelledby="tab-faq"
							role="tabpanel"
							tabindex="0"
						>
							<h3 class="sr-only">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

							<dl>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Q1: What type of websites do you build?
								</dt>
								<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
									<p>
										A: We build everything from business websites and landing
										pages to blogs, portfolios, and custom web apps.
									</p>
								</dd>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Q2: How long does it take to develop a website?
								</dt>
								<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
									<p>
										A: It depends on the complexity. A simple site can be ready
										in 1–2 weeks, while more advanced projects may take 4–8
										weeks or more.
									</p>
								</dd>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Q3: Is Astro a good choice for SEO?
								</dt>
								<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
									<p>
										A: Absolutely. Astro pre-renders pages into static HTML,
										which is highly performant and search-engine friendly.
									</p>
								</dd>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Q4: Why use Vercel for deployment?
								</dt>
								<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
									<p>
										A: Vercel offers global edge deployment, automatic scaling,
										Git integration, and incredibly fast hosting — making it
										ideal for modern web projects.
									</p>
								</dd>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Q5: Will my website be mobile-friendly?
								</dt>
								<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
									<p>
										A: Yes, all our websites are designed to be fully responsive
										and look great on phones, tablets, and desktops.
									</p>
								</dd>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Q6: Do you provide hosting and domain registration?
								</dt>
								<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
									<p>
										A: We assist with setting up hosting (e.g., on Vercel) and
										can guide you through domain registration, although the
										actual domain purchase is done through a registrar.
									</p>
								</dd>
							</dl>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
	</div>
</Layout>
